<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pollution Data Dashboard</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Pollution Data Dashboard</h1>
    
    <!-- Research Questions and Query Buttons -->
    <div class="query-section">
      <h2>Research Questions</h2>
      <div class="query-description">
        <p>1. Which cities rank highest in terms of overall AQI values?</p>
        <a href="/city-rankings" class="query-button">City Rankings by AQI</a>
      </div>
      <div class="query-description">
        <p>2. What is the average urban AQI value for each country, and how do they rank globally?</p>
        <a href="/national-urban-aq" class="query-button">National Urban Air Quality</a>
      </div>
      <div class="query-description">
        <p>3. Across all cities, which pollutant shows the highest average AQI value?</p>
        <a href="/dominant-pollutants" class="query-button">Dominant Pollutants</a>
      </div>
      <div class="query-description">
        <p>4. In which cities is the AQI value for NO2 consistently higher than that for CO?</p>
        <a href="/pollutant-prevalence" class="query-button">Pollutant Prevalence in Cities</a>
      </div>
      <div class="query-description">
        <p>5. For the cities with the highest pollution levels, how do the average AQI values for different pollutants compare?</p>
        <a href="/urban-centers-profile" class="query-button">Pollution Profiles of Urban Centers</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
